    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">Marienbad is a strategy game where matches are put on a table. Each of your turns, you can take either 1, 2 or 3 matches. You <strong>lose</strong> if you take the last match.<br>Alice and Bob are playing the game of Marienbad with <var>n</var> matches. Given who begins and how many matches were removed each turn, tell if <const>Bob</const> or <const>Alice</const> won. If you can't tell who won, print <const>Nobody</const>.<br><br>Note that if only one match is left, you can tell who will win.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong><var>beginner</var>:</strong> The name of the first player<br><strong><var>n</var>:</strong> The number of matches at the beginning<br><strong><var>r</var>:</strong> Number of rounds to come<br><strong><var>r</var> space separated numbers:</strong> The number of matches removed (either <const>1</const>,<const>2</const> or <const>3</const>)</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\">Either <const>Alice</const>, <const>Bob</const> or <const>Nobody</const></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\"><var>beginner</var> is either <const>Bob</const> or <const>Alice</const><br><strong>10</strong> &le; <var>n</var> &le; <strong>100</strong><br><strong>3</strong> &le; <var>r</var> &le; <strong>100</strong></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">Bob\n13\n6\n3 2 3 2 2 1</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">Bob</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
